
---

**APIPulseNet**  
**Description:**  
Continuously probes APIs and builds a pulse graph of response time and availability, designed for multi-endpoint monitoring.

```markdown
# APIPulseNet - API Response Pulse Tracker

APIPulseNet captures real-time changes in availability and builds latency heatmaps to compare endpoint health over time.

## Features
- Endpoint health graphing  
- Pulse and downtime alerts  
- CSV and JSON exports

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/APIPulseNet.git
cd APIPulseNet
python monitor.py
